title: Making Your Mission Possible with Tim Tebow
description:
Life is all about identifying your mission — but what if you don't know where to start? You may know Tim Tebow from his remarkable football career, but his life's mission extends far beyond the field. Judah and Chelsea sit down with Tim to discuss his latest book, Mission Possible — and unpack the importance of following your convictions, what it means to live a meaningful life, and how giving to others can be the greatest gift to yourself.
